and say, this is scary, we need to do something

00:16:22.832 --> 00:16:28.030
about this. This is a moral imparity. What is, what is behind that?

00:16:28.030 --> 00:16:30.105
&gt;&gt; Aside from the movie Gatika,

00:16:30.105 --> 00:16:34.137
which I think is behind a lot of it. It's a very scary movie.

