will probably never effect me? No, it seems unfair.

00:17:25.521 --> 00:17:26.959
&gt;&gt; Unfair.

00:17:26.959 --> 00:17:31.290
&gt;&gt; which is, you know, a very high-minded, ethical and legal concept.

